title: Moscow Regrets Protest Dispersed in Montenegro Amid NATO Expansion
text: Earlier in the day, media reported that the Montenegro police had dispersed the campsite of the opposition, which was staging an indefinite protest in front of the parliament. The protesters were calling for the resignation of the government, accusing it of corruption and undemocratic practices. ...
